response.overview: Desultory - Live at Hellfest 2015 is a raw and blistering capture of the legendary Swedish death metal band’s performance at one of Europe’s most iconic metal festivals. Showcasing their signature blend of melodic aggression and relentless energy, this set is a must-watch for fans of classic death metal and Hellfest’s chaotic spirit.
response.title: Desultory - Live at Hellfest 2015
